MEANWHILE, FRED KLEINMAN GETS
A BULLET BETWEEN THE EYES.

22:59.839 --> 23:01.421
THAT'S YOUR -- THAT'S YOUR
VERSION OF HUMANE?

23:01.421 --> 23:02.672
I GOT NEWS FOR YOU,
DR. PIERCE.

23:02.672 --> 23:03.843
THERE WAS NOBODY
ON THE GRASSY KNOLL,

23:03.843 --> 23:06.055
THERE ARE
