23:06.055 --> 23:08.468
AND THE CIA DID NOT ASSASSINATE
NICOLAI ZALESKY

23:08.468 --> 23:09.679
OR YOUR FRIEND.

23:09.679 --> 23:12.351
DANIEL? A WORD?

